fragment_downloaded_cb({"url": "Feature-autodetection.html#coverage", "fragment": "Coverage \nWhen doing a code coverage build Meson will check the existance of binaries gcovr lcov and genhtml. If the first one is found it will create targets called coverage text and coverage xml. If the latter two are found it generates the target coverage html. You can then generate coverage reports just by calling e.g. ninja coverage xml. \n"});